  <brief_title>Impact of HIV and Its Treatment on Reverse Cholesterol Transport</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of HIV Infection and Treatment With Highly Active Antiretroviral Therapy on Reverse Cholesterol Transport</official_title>
