  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the effect of treatment of HIV infection with highly active antiretroviral
      therapy on individual steps of reverse cholesterol transport, endothelial function and
      intima-media thickness in HIV patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
