    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male patients with HIV infection (3 groups of 50 patients each)

          -  HIV infected patients, na誰ve to ARV therapy and not likely to need to commence therapy
             for the duration of follow-up (12 months)

          -  HIV-infected patients, PI na誰ve, initiating therapy with PI-containing HAART (ARV
             na誰ve or NNRTI experienced changing to PI regimen)

          -  HIV-infected patients na誰ve to ARV therapy, initiating NNRTI-containing regimen

        Exclusion criteria

          -  Treatment with any form of lipid lowering drugs, including fish oils.

          -  Body Mass Index greater than 27.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
